The '''Alliance Credit''' was the official currency of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]]. Officially, the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] declared that the Alliance Credit had no value, but Alliance sympathizers usually accepted the Alliance Credit at face value. On the [[Black market/Legends|black market]], the general exchange rate was twenty-five Alliance Credits for one [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|Imperial Credit]].

